        <h2 class="heading"><Strong>SKILLS</Strong></h2>
        <div class="skill">
            <h3>Cloud Computing</h3>
            <p>Cloud computing is a powerful skill that involves managing and storing data on remote servers accessible via the internet. It includes mastering platforms like AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud, understanding virtualization, and managing databases and networks. It’s about enabling scalable, flexible, and cost-effective solutions from anywhere in the world.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill">
            <h3>Designing</h3>
            <p>Designing is a creative skill that involves conceptualizing and producing visual solutions to communicate ideas. It encompasses understanding user needs, creating wireframes, choosing color schemes, typography, and layout designs. Proficiency in tools like Adobe Creative Suite and Sketch, along with an eye for aesthetics and detail, are key aspects of this skill.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill">
            <h3>Web Developer</h3>
            <p>Web development is a technical skill that involves creating and maintaining websites or web applications. It includes proficiency in languages like HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, understanding of server-side languages like Python or Node.js, knowledge of databases, and familiarity with web protocols and API integration. It's about creating functional, user-friendly digital experiences.</p>
        </div>
